{"tid":2052102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[杜湯夫婦案] 刑事偵緝警員廖凱欣指自己從未去過西區又唔識睇地圖 所以指唔到自己當時位置","createTime":"2020-06-05T09:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T12:07:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":166,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"ade89255d83fcdfcf79000bf30331932cc33f88f","tid":2052102,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"控方傳召當日有份處理杜依蘭及李姓少女的的刑事偵緝警員廖凱欣作供。廖的手寫供詞稱，當日於德輔道西推進時，目睹「行車綫兩旁行人路上的路人向不同方向散開」，她今指「路人」即「路上的人」，認同行人路上有不肯定是否示威者的人夾雜其中。辯方要求她於地圖上標出自己當時的位置，她一度站立回憶當時方位惟未能成功，遂向辯方表示歉意，稱自己「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁大個女都未去過西區</span></strong>」，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">地圖真係唔係好識睇</span></strong>」。<br />\n<br />\n其他詳情 :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074203&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=938aca68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074203&h=452103d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074203</a>"},{"pid":"7cac0f24659541bbd43aeeb9077e268934d97a88","tid":2052102,"uid":185656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3c5f65e7c5cf48cbe604c079175d8462581c28","tid":2052102,"uid":18948,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"未去過西區點喺現場拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b94b566a53bc44afe686ebbaf7624d36681b078","tid":2052102,"uid":130195,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"睇到我成個人黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe78cf61c23aedb7c81970ef8c17fa03088d7afa","tid":2052102,"uid":285261,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:16:47.000Z","m